item.title: Intro
item.description: Heading level 3 !Disclaimer! These are just my personal views, opinions, and rants about the nursing field. I’m definitely no expert writer and even with the two decades of experience in the field, I do not make any claims to be the foremost expert in this field . What I’m hoping for is funny but respectful comments, constructive criticism and any valuable input. I’m hoping to grow , become better by interacting with my peers on this forum.
